Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Beast Invasion\Nepisode 3
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ghostly aura calls to\Nthe evil spirits around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These past visions\Nare disgusting to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begone, dead creatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where\Nthey failed to kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how could they\Nwith Maitreya's power?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were just a normal man and\Nwoman. They weren't like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother! Now you and\NI will become one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And infinite power\Nwill be mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't give birth to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your power is the source\Nof my power, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.73,0:04:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You forced yourself into me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make up things!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.11,0:04:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why do you drip\Nwith this warm wetness?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:05:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know you want to\Nbecome one with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... Why can't I move?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother! Why?\NWhy?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHY?!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.95,0:07:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her mind's synched all\Nthe way with the vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay. Just a little tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Demon Beast reading,\Nall right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its body was dying.\NIt must have made it here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its consciousness is still active\Nin part of its body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.73,0:07:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're to settle this,\Nwe have to finish it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother! Don't abandon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that voice again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:08:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was over.\NI thought it was over!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.93,0:08:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want\Nto remember again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to forget!\NI have to forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Demon Beast hasn't contacted\NKayo yet. Standing guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Beast spawn section\Napportioned!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was one of the\Nmother body's classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pursuing fertilizing carrier body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.55,0:09:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Kayo.\NWhy don't you come over?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.97,0:09:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father's gone to Oyama for\Na memorial service for Maitreya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on... Oh,\Nit won't work, Muneto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.52,0:09:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least hearing your voice\Nmakes me feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Ever since we did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I hear your voice,\NI can't control myself!.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go to my parents\Nthis late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.20,0:09:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, help me forget all\Nthese awful memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.37,0:09:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't,\NI don't know what I'll do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:10:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo... Just remember\Nhow it felt for the two of us to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.67,0:10:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...be wrapped\Nin Maitreya's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.88,0:10:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt... your warmth\Ninside of me... Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, as you flowed\Nwith your own warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.89,0:10:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thrust into you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kayo! I want to suck\Nyour breasts again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.23,0:10:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your finger...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you! Oh, god,\NI'm burning up for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo, make that sound again!\NI can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.57,0:10:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!\NIt's embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.24,0:10:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.28,0:10:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto, I feel like...\NI'm going to...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.59,0:10:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body's doing this by itself.\NDon't hate me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not usually this sex crazed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.28,0:11:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of my sisters is with her.\NShe still hasn't been attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her body is calling forth\Nthose visions, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.55,0:11:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.01,0:11:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interplanetary Mutual\NObservation Agent: Ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.31,0:11:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been dispatched here\Nto follow up...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.22,0:11:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...on your failure to\Nfinish off the Demon Beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.94,0:11:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Demon Beast is\Ntrying to revive itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it isn't over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:12:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because I couldn't protect\NKayo from it in the first place..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that she's the way she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.00,0:12:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now it's back...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo stole your heart while\Nyou were on this assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.32,0:12:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you couldn't fulfill\Nyour duty as an I MO agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a student now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.07,0:13:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just forget\Nall that horrible stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, when I heard\Nthey'd closed the school...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't your fault.\NDon't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know,\Nbut then I think about...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...all the classmates who were\Nsacrificed to that Demon Beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.17,0:13:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about last night.\NBut why'd you hang up like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.97,0:13:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...\NDad came home, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Demon Beast is\Ntrying to revive itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.10,0:13:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lay this on Kayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother... Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.13,0:14:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her scent... I want the warmth\NI smell flowing from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After what happened, our class\Ntransferred away bit by bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But besides that,\Nwhat happened to me last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even tell Muneto about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.68,0:15:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again? No, not now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo's stolen your heart.\NYour mission isn't over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.19,0:15:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a student now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.53,0:15:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, you are my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.25,0:15:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the only one who\NI can become one with in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.67,0:15:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only being with you\Ncan I be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My class! I'm going to\Nbe late for my class!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.95,0:16:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.29,0:16:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh, yes...\N- No, you're not like Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:17:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like her...\NYou're not! You're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.80,0:17:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to save Kayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.86,0:17:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must gather together\Nmy body's parts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.53,0:17:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring Mother to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.36,0:17:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.24,0:18:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis has changed\Nsince we got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Be a little more showy.\NWorry about the Earthier."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.08,0:18:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's never said\Nanything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.62,0:18:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She made us set\Nthe Buster Guns to 50%.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she's all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.47,0:18:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.10,0:18:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a little part of the Demon\NBeast has that much life force?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.27,0:18:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange... Ms. Satomi's never\Nbeen late or missed her class.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she's sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo, do you want to come down\Nto Shinjuku with us later?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.43,0:19:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to a burger\Nplace in Shintoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Class 1-3 from Meisei's\Nall split up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the girls from the\Nclass are getting together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo... Maybe we should\Nplay it safe today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.53,0:19:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Muneto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all just worried about\Nhow depressed Kayo's gotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.78,0:19:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right.\NI don't want to be rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.62,0:19:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised them that\NI'll bring you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.12,0:19:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the only women to come here\Nfrom the other school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.67,0:19:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We even asked Ms. Satomi to come\Nsince she transferred here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.13,0:19:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been so nice,\Ntrying to comfort us since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can all just relax\Nand have a good time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's decided!\NThe more, the merrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:20:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think\Nit sounds fun, Muneto?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.82,0:20:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what can be keeping\NMs. Satomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.87,0:20:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Satomi...\NCould she have been...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.72,0:20:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. Everyone\Nshould have been here by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.55,0:20:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.\NI know they'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.27,0:21:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.61,0:21:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo lied to us!\NShe said this thing was dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.95,0:21:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Satomi, why just us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.92,0:21:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our class... must be cursed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.59,0:21:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.32,0:22:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.98,0:22:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kill the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.02,0:22:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.74,0:22:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erase!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.99,0:23:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.37,0:23:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's it gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.37,0:23:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo! It must have smelled\Nthe mother's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.04,0:23:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides that, its body...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.96,0:24:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Demon Beast is exploding\Nwith growth hormones.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.97,0:24:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it doesn't combine\Nwith Kayo properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.43,0:24:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it'll just keep on growing\Nbigger and bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.10,0:24:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.77,0:24:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let it get to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.35,0:24:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.73,0:24:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.73,0:24:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.83,0:24:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Satomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.92,0:24:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up! Speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.09,0:24:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.76,0:24:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save yourself, Kayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.43,0:24:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Demon Beast's about\Nto regenerate itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.10,0:24:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.02,0:24:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He needs women to regenerate.\NAnd he's after you!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.11,0:25:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.78,0:25:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.56,0:25:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was once able to gain\NMaitreya's powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.85,0:25:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and defeat the Demon Beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.19,0:25:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now it's after Kayo and\Nthe whole human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.15,0:25:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love is power. The power\Nto drive evil away.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.53,0:25:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maitreya taught us that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.37,0:25:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But can I save Kayo,\Nthe way I am now?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.70,0:25:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have the right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.33,0:25:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.46,0:25:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in yourself!.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.04,0:26:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yours and Kayo's heart\Nbecame one, that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.22,0:26:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was love.\NI know this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.43,0:26:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.14,0:26:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a woman born\Nonly to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.22,0:26:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love, friendship,\Nfeelings of kinship...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.89,0:26:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All outside of duty\Nhas been forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.52,0:26:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe I never knew them at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.86,0:26:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was you two who\Nreturned these feelings to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.20,0:26:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The image of you two\Njoined in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.91,0:26:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how!\NHow I know of your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.46,0:26:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How I know of the\Npotential power within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.25,0:26:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With your feelings\Nas torn apart as they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.92,0:26:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you won't be able to stop\Nthe Demon Beast or save Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.43,0:26:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in yourself!.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.85,0:26:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to feel the love\Nyou have for Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.98,0:26:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.48,0:27:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.50,0:27:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.63,0:27:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.96,0:27:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.93,0:27:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you contact Ash, Dee?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.93,0:27:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my visor!\NI can't contact her without it!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.60,0:27:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could manage\Nif we had the Buster Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.94,0:27:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.53,0:27:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.96,0:28:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.05,0:28:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's\Ngoing on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.27,0:28:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo... Kayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.35,0:29:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!\NI didn't mean to peep.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.06,0:29:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I can't get your help...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.36,0:29:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we'll have to do everything\Nwe can to stop the Demon Beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.32,0:29:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I face a life\Nor death battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.74,0:29:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I like to purify my body\Nwith water. Just a habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.75,0:29:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.\NI can't believe in myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.42,0:29:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I really bring\Nmy love for her out?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.75,0:29:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way we felt\Nwhen we joined that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.38,0:29:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like\Nit never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.05,0:29:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even feel\NMaitreya's power...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.09,0:29:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong. Maitreya's power\Nis sleeping within your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.56,0:29:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That power comes when your heart\Ncalls out to love and protect each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.19,0:29:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is Maitreya's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.61,0:29:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without your consciousness,\NKayo cannot save herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.45,0:29:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.37,0:30:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.46,0:30:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Train now arriving in station.\NPlease stand behind the white line.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.77,0:30:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The damn thing doesn't know\Nwhen to quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.11,0:30:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you helping me?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.82,0:30:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.19,0:30:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do is dodge him\Ntill Sis gets here with Muneto.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.49,0:30:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We three can't handle\Nthis Demon Beast alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.78,0:30:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.79,0:30:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.46,0:30:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Stop!\NThis is your duty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.55,0:31:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretend I'm Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.85,0:31:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm to synch my clairvoyance\Nto give you the feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.18,0:31:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you two had in my vision,\Nyou have to think I'm Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.48,0:31:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo... Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.20,0:31:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open your feelings.\NThink back to that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.75,0:31:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.19,0:31:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.62,0:32:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.03,0:33:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment,\Nwhen I learned of your love...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.33,0:33:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I learned another way\Na woman can live her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.00,0:33:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To see something\Nbeyond death and battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.96,0:33:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a poor substitute for the love\Nyou and Kayo have tuned so finely!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.34,0:33:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels so strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.97,0:33:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this power I feel in\Nthe depths of my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.18,0:33:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the power of Maitreya?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.31,0:33:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could almost pierce Kayo\Nwith the love I have for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.31,0:33:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body, it's getting hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.67,0:34:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if\NBB and Kayo are okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.35,0:34:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that big?!\NI better find Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.58,0:35:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to hide here\Ntill Ash and Muneto come.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.30,0:35:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're late!\NAnd I can't contact my two sisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.09,0:35:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kayo okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.68,0:35:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the Demon Beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.30,0:35:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a giant lump\Nof growing flesh now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.01,0:35:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo's still okay. We just\Nhave to find her before it can!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.61,0:35:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It found us!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.74,0:35:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found her! Found her!\NFound her! Found her!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.99,0:35:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.04,0:35:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.13,0:35:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring you with me,\NMother!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.43,0:36:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother! At last...\NAt last we can become one!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.27,0:36:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting worse. It's\Nregenerating just by touching her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.61,0:36:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he gets her completely,\Nwe'll never get her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.28,0:36:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.74,0:36:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First I have to get\NKayo away from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.62,0:36:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you and she have to use\NMaitreya's power to finish it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.33,0:36:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha! Go to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.17,0:36:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, I have waited so long\Nfor this day...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.51,0:36:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MOTHER!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.01,0:36:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I don't want to!\NNot with you! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.65,0:36:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.16,0:37:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No use. Can't break\Nthrough by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.21,0:37:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.50,0:37:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BB! Dee!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.51,0:37:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to enter\Nour final mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.89,0:37:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Final mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.85,0:37:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.77,0:37:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.44,0:37:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Muneto.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.11,0:37:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to use the\Nlast of our power to free Kayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.91,0:37:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. Because of you, I was\Nable to come as a real woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.78,0:37:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only wish I could have\Nshared that with my sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.16,0:37:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ash! What are...\NWhat are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.04,0:37:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first time you've\Ncalled me by my name, Muneto...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.09,0:37:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Ash! Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.72,0:37:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Kayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.76,0:38:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YOU CAN'T DIE!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.90,0:38:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is useless.\NMother belongs to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.49,0:38:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.21,0:38:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.84,0:38:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.80,0:38:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.64,0:38:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.\NNow lend me your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.11,0:38:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just about to regenerate...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.95,0:38:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.70,0:39:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.31,0:39:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So many victims\Nbecause I lacked the strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.69,0:39:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ash...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.70,0:39:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.62,0:39:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.33,0:39:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't do anything.\NAnything at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.75,0:39:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.36,0:40:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother... Mother...\NMother... Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.50,0:40:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a dream. Thank god.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.39,0:40:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank god. Just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.69,0:40:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, I am immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.07,0:41:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will keep comihg back to life\Nagain and again!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.74,0:41:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a dream!\NIt is!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.29,0:41:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is a dream,\Nthen come save me, Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.42,0:41:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.80,0:41:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MAITREYA!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.01,0:41:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KAYO!!!
